Package guiTeacher.interfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Clickable
    A Visible object that can be clicked on.
    Dragable
    A visible object that can be dragged.
    DrawInstructions
    Used by CustomImageButtons to define the appearance of the buttons
    FileRequester
    Must be implemented by Screens that use FileOpenButtons
    FocusController
    A focus controller shifts the focus of the scrolling pane.
    KeyedComponent
    Must be implemented by any Component that responds to keyed entry
    Scrollable
    Must be implemented by Components that respond to Scrolling actions (mouse wheel)
    Task
    Must be implement in order to use a progress bar
    TextComponent
    An interface for any Component that has a text value that can be retrieved
    Visible
    Everything that can be shown within a window must implement this interface
